  "Description": {
    "English": "A high-detail sonar device, capable of upgrading the scanner technology aboard a Nautilon-class submarine to <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span> levels, pinning to the HUD all information typically revealed by the Analysis Visor.<br><br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> to activate the High-Power Sonar.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种高细节声纳设备，能把大鹦鹉螺级潜水艇上的扫描仪技术升级至<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>水平，在HUD上显示与分析面甲相同的信息。<br><br>按<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>激活高功率声纳。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种高细节声纳设备，能把大鹦鹉螺级潜水艇上的扫描仪技术升级至分析面甲水平。<br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> 启动高功率声纳。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "可呈現高度細節的聲納裝置，可以將巡洋龍級別潛艇上的掃描器科技升級為<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>等級，將其釘選至抬頭顯示器即可查看所有分析護目鏡所示資訊。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> 啟用高功率聲納。"
  },
